Summary_Section.Summary: Seekster is an online platform that connects blue-collar service providers to consumers in Thailand. While it provides an easy way to book cleaning and other services for homes and offices, for the workers, it provides a deterministic and stable source of jobs. Seekster streamelines the process of ordering, paying, and rating the service providers.

Points: A paid, fulltime staff team of 20
Sign up residents and offices in Tier-1 cities of Thailand
Run promotion campaigns to use the cleaning packages from Seekster
Oversee the success of jobs and manage payments
Encourage and receive ratings for each of the jobs completed
#of of jobs successfully connected with the service provider(s) needed

A database of workers sorted by their reputation score
Additonal income opportunity for the workers
Time savings for the customers because of the jobs done by Seekster

I bet we all have seen some flyers posted on walls or electricity poles advertising services or looking to recruit a maids or technicians. What’s happening in the fragmented market of service is about the space between customers and service providers where customer have no centralized data of the reliable service provider’s whereabouts. Some may have a regular service provider that may be reliable but will have to wait for the queue for 1 month. The pricing in the service market is fluctuated and differs by each provider making it a tough decision for customer to decide. On the other hand service provider is living in a risky condition where jobs came inconsistently.

Points.Description: Seekster sees the problem and willing to tackle. We want you to be able to find reliable service provider that can track the background. Seekster curated each service provider and secure their information. We design the system as per Crowd Sourcing model where jobs will be distributed and you can be serviced as long as the service provider is presented in your area.

Listing.Title: DTAC - Total Access Communication Public Company Limited
Listing.Description: DTAC Accelerate is Thailand's No. 1 Accelerator house. Our mission is to seek out potential startups. And push these startup. Grow up fast We believe that startup Thailand. Can expand the business to the world. And that is our mission. To create the next Unicorn of South East Asia, we have already invested in 34 teams from the past 5 batches worth a total of over $ 3.5 billion. 70% of the startups we invested. The investment is continued from investors in both Thailand and the region. We are one of the most accredited Accelerator houses in Southeast Asia. At present, our startup projects are in Exit 1, Series A 4 and Seed 17.
RoleInvolved: DTAC connects Investors from both Thailand and outside to invest in the South Asian Staurtups. DTAC also provides business strategy and executing guidance legeraging the pool of seasoned entrepreneurs and mentors.

Listing.Title: 500 TukTuks
Listing.Description: “500 TukTuks”, a $10M USD micro-fund focused on promising startups, managed by new 500 investing partners Krating Poonpol and Moo Natavudh. Why the name TukTuks? Well they are small, lean, fast, agile, and dangerous. JUST LIKE STARTUPS. They are excited to take a trip through the winding roads of Thailand to discover smart, badass entrepreneurs.
RoleInvolved: 500 sees an opportunity to invest early and often into the next generation of Thailand’s most promising startups and empower them with best of Silicon Valley’s education, thinking, talent, and money to provide unfair advantage in the local market. 500 will be the first major SV accelerator and seed stage investor in the local Thai market and founders will gain access to our global network of high-value mentors and 2,000+ founders. 500 will look to invest in not just companies that can succeed in the local Asian market, but through its accelerator, find and work with Thai companies that can succeed in the US and global market.

Listing.Title: Ananda Development
Listing.Description: Ananda Development Public Company Limited was founded in 1999 by Chanond Ruangkritya.Ananda has continued to develop its brands and its unique Urban Living Solutions, resulting in it becoming the leading developer of residential projects in close proximity to mass transit stations in Bangkok. Ananda achieved this success through its branded products such as IDEO, first launched in 2007 and IDEO MOBI first launched in the first quarter of 2012. Its stylish, modern and high quality, yet affordable products have led to Ananda becoming one of the best known property development brands in Bangkok.
RoleInvolved: Seekster will be a preferred partner for sourcing service-providers to the Ananda Development projects and customers.
